{"tid":965020,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打覺得高朋滿座比人低估得好緊要？","createTime":"2019-01-01T17:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T10:15:20.000Z","uid":92376,"like":37,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f739959b7a7ac52ce8877b77ecad6b36019f894f","tid":965020,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:20:49.000Z","msg":"呢套野當年可能跟住皆大歡喜播所以有啲被比下去 但實際唔係咁弱<br />\n首先有兩位演藝界好戲老師級人馬<br />\nking sir鍾景輝做爺爺<br />\n仲有阿旦鄭丹瑞做老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加埋果時仲算得上風韻猶存既<br />\n伍姑娘做阿旦老婆<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有未紅未串<br />\n未會擺款既思捷做舅仔<br />\n果陣佢做毒撚角色<br />\n都幾入型入格架<br />\n<br />\n曹永廉做二佬幾襯佢+高B果時夠青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係就係大口喱個柒樣趕客左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外仲開創左依家sitcom<br />\n唔顯示集數只顯示當集主題既先河<br />\n起到指標性既作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知點解<br />\n家陣講起差既處境果時實有人講高朋<br />\n啲人會唔會太低估呢套野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e0bc178003bf4e6294a25329c38119b2292694","tid":965020,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:22:29.000Z","msg":"點睇？連登太多bb無人睇過高朋？"},{"pid":"2e004db82fa5e883c10e934d05f2a8f891360a99","tid":965020,"uid":53254,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"對king sir同蛋冇好感"},{"pid":"2749a6d1a56484f93cb4618d0f3befab220303af","tid":965020,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2e004db82fa5e883c10e934d05f2a8f891360a99","tid":965020,"uid":53254,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"對king sir同蛋冇好感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"因為佢地比人感覺太學院派？"},{"pid":"26431d6a0645fb27c217ce0aaac18bb14a88abf4","tid":965020,"uid":92376,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T17:25:16.000Z","msg":"da da de da da de da 